data.description: Discover this stunning residence in a sought-after community! This thoughtfully crafted 3-bedroom, 1.75-bath home seamlessly blends industrial and contemporary design elements. The open floor plan features tasteful wood accents, complemented by exquisite quartz kitchen countertops and tile backsplashes. Grab a drink at the coffee/wine bar and walk outside to the inviting outdoor covered patio with fireplace, providing a perfect setting for relaxation with a view of the Organ Mountains.The primary bedroom boasts a spacious walk-in closet with built-in storage and convenient barn door access. Enjoy well-designed lighting, polished concrete flooring, and a stylish bathroom complete with double sinks and a generously-sized walk-in shower, all powered by the home's efficient tankless water heater. This residence is a perfect synthesis of modern aesthetics and functional design and conveniently located near Red Hawk Golf Course, NASA, White Sands, shopping, and schools.  Don't wait, schedule a showing now!
